Class CatalogController

  • java.lang.Object
    • internetkaufhaus.controller.CatalogController

  • @Controller
 @SessionAttributes(value="cart")
public class CatalogController
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the catalog controller. It controls the catalog. Or does it catalog the controller? You never know... In this class you may find the controllers for the catalog and article pages, should you choose to look for them.
